.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

5 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, monopoly, bridge, backgammon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, surfing, climbing, weightlifting, snowboarding
House: craftsman, townhouse, palace, cottage, art-deco
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pokermaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, firefighter, electrician, security-guard, accountant
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person playing monopoly
2. the person who's sport is swedish is the electrician
3. the person who's sport is surfing is the cottage house
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing bridge
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the townhouse house
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the firefighter
7. the person playing backgammon is the dunhill-smoker
8. the palace house is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the mechanic
11. the accountants is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the pokermaster-smoker is the craftsman house
13. the person who's sport is climbing is the prince-smoker
14. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person playing poker
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the art-deco house

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Game		|    backgammon	|     poker	|      monopoly	|     mah-jongg	|     bridge	|
| Sport	|   weightlifting	|    surfing	|    handball	|    climbing	|    swedish	|
| Job		|     mechanic	|    accountant	|     firefighter	|     security-guard	|      electrician	|
| House	|    art-deco	|     cottage	|     palace	|    townhouse	|      craftsman	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   pokermaster	|
